{"tid":993564,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好似喺連登第一個美式炸雞錘教學","createTime":"2019-01-24T04:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T07:24:11.000Z","uid":227262,"like":85,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa95c4c22a7d3fb953d20d53ff27ea0299983f8","tid":993564,"uid":227262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"先同大家講句SORRY,因為原本無打算開POST,所以極度少圖,不過跟住我簡單嘅步驟應該成品都會一樣,如果反應好,下次會多圖甚至有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n材料:    炸雞錘最重要嘅梗喺雞錘(盡量揀新鮮雞)*8隻<br />\n            大量油(想顏色好睇就棕櫚油,健康就芥花籽油)<br />\n<br />\n醃漿:    薑泥*2大湯匙  <br />\n            蒜泥*2大湯匙 <br />\n            辣椒仔*4-5條 <br />\n            青椒*2條 <br />\n            白胡椒*2茶匙 <br />\n            花椒*2茶匙 <br />\n            八角*4粒 <br />\n            蒜粉*2大湯匙 <br />\n            粟米粉*2大湯匙 <br />\n            牛奶*250毫升左右<br />\n            鹽*2茶匙        <br />\n<br />\n炸粉:    中筋麵粉*2杯<br />\n            糯米粉*2大湯匙 <br />\n            黑粉蒜粉紅椒粉鹽*各1大湯匙 <br />\n            白胡椒*3大湯匙 <br />\n<br />\n做法極度簡單:<br />\n               1.先洗乾淨雞錘,去血水,吸乾水分,雞皮粘手為之乾<br />\n               2.將所有醃料打成蓉,然後溝牛奶攪勻<br />\n               3.將雞浸落醃醬,然後落兩大湯匙粟米粉攪拌,醃過夜<br />\n               4.拎出黎上炸粉<br />\n               5.首先220度炸兩分鐘,等表面先熟鎖住肉汁,攤3分鐘<br />\n               6.攤完之後就180度炸5-6分鐘炸熟埋入面<br />\n               7.最後用最高溫炸30秒至1分鐘,逼油同令表皮酥脆<br />\n<br />\n上粉秘訣:<br />\n               第一層粉要輕壓,然後浸水2秒浸濕第一層粉,然後再輕輕拍第二層粉,就做到起粒嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n成品:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X9B3PVD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX9B3PVD.jpg&h=b95bf065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映: 他他醬<br />\n材料:     雞蛋2隻<br />\n             白胡椒粉 10 g<br />\n             麻油 20 g<br />\n             蛋黃醬 150 g<br />\n             酸青瓜1-2條<br />\n             醬油 15 g<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTT9Lwe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTT9Lwe.jpg&h=ee968ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做法:  全部打碎撈勻<br />\n成品:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgtauYe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgtauYe.jpg&h=05573847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b103fb2cefcee30c55c213f0f2275bff934f6a3","tid":993564,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8095add59583be34aead7db24e2df8c6ffc56a6b","tid":993564,"uid":31300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"有料到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32269c146c4af10f0adf67113023a7e080add70","tid":993564,"uid":158411,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_lyhqk1YnsS1qjirgz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_lyhqk1YnsS1qjirgz.gif&h=65b30cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"832adb47e699e74d231a579f505ae338cf092efb","tid":993564,"uid":145730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e32269c146c4af10f0adf67113023a7e080add70","tid":993564,"uid":158411,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_lyhqk1YnsS1qjirgz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_lyhqk1YnsS1qjirgz.gif&h=65b30cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8d11df0b05b5cef5608770fbcf2e49c862a4bf","tid":993564,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"睇落正 但感覺唔好食"}